          "outcome": "Pass",
          "summary": "Criterion 1 (install writes executable pre-commit with managed-by marker): src/commands/hooks.rs:57 defines HOOK_MARKER as '# managed-by: req-hooks'; lines 203-213 write the hook body and call set_executable. Criterion 2 (uninstall removes only managed hooks): lines 164-178 check body.contains(HOOK_MARKER) before removing; skips unmanaged hooks. Criterion 3 (exits zero when no .req files staged): precommit_body() at line 83 generates shell that checks 'git diff --cached --name-only | grep -qE .req' and runs req validate only when .req files are staged, exiting cleanly otherwise. All three criteria are met."
        },
        "concluded": "2026-06-13T07:53:23.819057100Z",
        "concluded_commit": "7107cab238bf327eab0eb41a18956905b38e8d93",
