        "plan": "Inspect src/commands/hooks.rs for HOOK_MARKER, PRECOMMIT_BODY install/uninstall logic, and zero-staged-files exit; exercise installed binary in a temp git repo.",
        "statement": "All three criteria are met: hooks.rs installs an executable pre-commit containing HOOK_MARKER, uninstall removes only managed hooks, and the shell script exits zero when no .req files are staged. Confirmed by code inspection at src/commands/hooks.rs and behavioral exercise of the installed binary.",
