          "summary": "No dedicated automated test named req_0023_* exists in the test suite. Behavioral verification via installed binary: in a fresh temp git repo 'req hooks install' wrote .git/hooks/pre-commit containing '# managed-by: req-hooks' and ran req validate only when a .req file was staged; 'req hooks uninstall' removed the managed hook and left a non-managed hook untouched. Three criteria confirmed by direct exercise of the binary at HEAD 7107cab."
        },
        "verdict": "Pass"
      }
