      "title": "Resolve ID collisions after merge via req renumber",
      "updated": "2026-06-13T06:08:56.041448500Z",
      "validation": {
        "actor": "Tom",
        "analysis": {
          "actor": "Tom",
          "at": "2026-06-13T06:06:22.530838400Z",
          "outcome": "Pass",
          "summary": "Criterion 1 (no remaining duplicates after renumber): src/commands/renumber.rs:23-38 detects collisions by comparing creation-time/title against the base ref and assigns fresh IDs above next_id. Criterion 2 (links rewritten): apply_renames() lines 84-90 iterates all link targets and substitutes the new IDs. Criterion 3 (history entry recorded): lines 72-75 push a history entry noting the old ID. Criterion 4 (--dry-run prints without writing): lines 49-51 return early after printing planned renames when args.dry_run is true. All four criteria are met."
        },
