          "at": "2026-06-13T06:11:33.639909700Z",
          "outcome": "Pass",
          "summary": "Criterion 1 (--add-acceptance appends and records history): update.rs:55-58 pushes onto r.acceptance and records a +acceptance entry in changes. Criterion 2 (--remove-acceptance N removes and refuses out-of-range): update.rs:59-73 sorts/deduplicates indexes descending, returns Err if idx_1==0 or idx_1>r.acceptance.len(). Criterion 3 (--accept replaces first then --add-acceptance appends): update.rs:51-57 processes args.acceptance first (replace), then args.add_acceptance (append). Tested by req_0035_update_add_and_remove_acceptance_criteria (coverage_boost.rs) which passed at commit 7107cab."
        },
