        "statement": "Every acceptance criterion is met: the exclusive OS advisory lock (fs2) held across the full load-modify-save cycle ensures concurrent adds both land with distinct IDs; the lock is an OS-level advisory lock released automatically on process death with no stale sidecar; acquisition has a 30-second timeout with a clear error message (storage.rs line 308). Confirmed by passing tests req_0062_two_concurrent_adds_both_land_with_distinct_ids and req_0062_five_concurrent_adds_all_land_with_unique_ids at commit 7107cab23.",
