          "summary": "AC1 (markdown level-2/3 headings, partial-reject without abort unless strict): import.rs parse_markdown (line 165) splits on ## and ### headings; each candidate is validated individually; failures are collected in rejected and the loop continues unless --strict is set (line 72-83). AC2 (JSON re-allocates IDs): import.rs parse_json re-reads the flat array and assigns new IDs via project.allocate_id() (line 89), avoiding collision. AC3 (same validator as req add): line 64 calls validate::validate_requirement on each candidate before accepting it. AC4 (dry-run does not mutate): lines 88-96 gate the allocate+insert behind !args.dry_run; save is also gated at line 99. All four criteria are met."
