          "notes": "validation dossier concluded — Every acceptance criterion is met: repair without --force refuses when validation errors are present (repair.rs lines 26-42); repair --force re-signs and prints a one-line warning naming the surviving error count (lines 44-52); after force-repair the file loads and req validate is the sole channel for remaining errors. Confirmed by code review and live exercise against the installed binary at commit 7107cab23.",
