          "notes": "validation dossier concluded — All four acceptance criteria are satisfied at commit 7107cab. REQ_VALIDATE_LLM_CONCURRENCY controls the concurrency cap (validate.rs:585) with a default of 1 for safe backwards-compatible behaviour. Findings from parallel threads are sorted by id before emission (line 649) giving stable output regardless of completion order. Each hook call has an independent 10s timeout (validate.rs:1009) so one slow call does not delay others in a different chunk. The env var and its semantics are documented in req help env (help_text.rs:666).",
