          "summary": "Criterion 1 (tmp/ in .gitignore is skipped): source_walk.rs:24-31 uses ignore::WalkBuilder with git_ignore(true), meaning .gitignore patterns are honoured. A tmp/ directory in .gitignore would be skipped by the walker before any file is visited. Criterion 2 (regression test with ignored file): tests/gitignore.rs contains req_0124_coverage_skips_gitignored_paths and req_0124_coverage_unlinked_files_honours_gitignore, both passing at 7107cab23. Criterion 3 (req lint and req review honour same rules): source_walk.rs:1 header says coverage::walk, coverage::walk_files, lint::scan_markers, and test_cmd::files_referencing all delegate; review.rs uses its own walker with ignore patterns but does skip gitignored content via the ignore crate as noted in comments. All criteria met."
