          "outcome": "Pass",
          "summary": "Criterion 1 (req test list prints commit, outcome, kind, at, notes per record): test_cmd.rs:51-60 formats each record with t.at, short(&t.commit), t.outcome.as_str(), t.kind.as_str(), t.notes. Criterion 2 (--json emits records as an array): test_cmd.rs:43-45 serialises r.tests directly to JSON when args.json is set. Criterion 3 (empty set prints clear '(no test records)' line): test_cmd.rs:47-49 prints '(no test records)' when r.tests.is_empty(). Criterion 4 (req_test_list MCP returns records as JSON array, resolves short/padded id forms): mcp.rs:2498-2506 calls resolve_id() for id normalisation and returns serde_json::to_string_pretty(&r.tests) which is an empty array when tests is empty."
