          "kind": "Composition",
          "notes": "cites: req_0130_validate_warns_on_verified_with_failing_latest, req_0130_validate_does_not_fail_on_warning_only, req_0130_verified_with_pass_latest_clean — Fires on Verified+failing-latest; doesn't fire on Verified+passing-latest; exit code stays zero.",
          "outcome": "Pass"
        },
