          "summary": "Criterion 1 (comment line with multiple REQ ids credits every id): review.rs:217-224 uses any_req_re.find_iter() which returns ALL matches on a line including multiple REQ ids; each match is inserted into coverage_referenced. A line '// REQs: REQ-0008, REQ-0015' would yield two find_iter matches, crediting both. Criterion 2 (// REQs: REQ-0008, REQ-0015 marks file covered and references both): the broad any_req_re scan credits REQ-0008 and REQ-0015 to coverage_referenced; the comment-context gate marker_line_re at review.rs:168 also captures the first id so the file passes the markerless gate. Both criteria met."
        },
