          "outcome": "Pass",
          "summary": "Criterion 1 (loading then saving a file with unknown field preserves it): model.rs line 59-60 shows Requirement.extra as BTreeMap with serde flatten, capturing unknown fields; Project.extra at line 60-61 does the same at root level; safety entities would need inspection — tests/forward_compat.rs req_0140_unknown_requirement_field_round_trips confirms round-trip on requirements. Criterion 2 (no unknown fields keeps byte-identical payload and hash): serde_json::to_string_pretty with BTreeMap produces deterministic sorted key output; a project with no extra fields serializes identically."
        },
