          "actor": "Tom",
          "at": "2026-06-13T06:08:21.144323300Z",
          "outcome": "Pass",
          "summary": "Criterion 1 (saving over newer _schema_rev refused, file unchanged): storage.rs guard_schema_rev() at line 44 is called on load before integrity check; if on_disk > SCHEMA_REV it returns Err naming both revisions — load fails, so save is never reached, file is unchanged. Criterion 2 (files without _schema_rev treated as revision 0): line 45 uses .unwrap_or(0) when the field is absent — met."
        },
