        "opened_commit": "7107cab238bf327eab0eb41a18956905b38e8d93",
        "plan": "Inspect src/storage.rs guard_schema_rev() for newer-rev refusal and zero-default; verify save() injects _schema_rev into hashed payload; cite tests req_0141_save_refused_when_file_schema_rev_is_newer and req_0141_missing_schema_rev_is_treated_as_zero at 7107cab23.",
        "statement": "Every acceptance criterion is met: storage.rs guard_schema_rev() refuses to load a file whose _schema_rev exceeds SCHEMA_REV, naming both revisions in the error — since load fails the save is never reached and the file is left unchanged; files without _schema_rev are treated as revision 0 via .unwrap_or(0) at line 45, allowing normal saves. Confirmed by passing tests req_0141_save_refused_when_file_schema_rev_is_newer and req_0141_missing_schema_rev_is_treated_as_zero at commit 7107cab23.",
        "testing": {
