          "summary": "Automated tests req_0141_save_refused_when_file_schema_rev_is_newer and req_0141_missing_schema_rev_is_treated_as_zero both passed at commit 7107cab238bf327eab0eb41a18956905b38e8d93. First test forges _schema_rev=9999, verifies the next add exits non-zero with a schema-rev mismatch message, and confirms the file is byte-identical after the refusal. Second test strips _schema_rev and verifies a subsequent mutation succeeds and restores the stamp."
