        "A filter (e.g. --not-genuine) restricts the report to items whose verification is not a genuine passing dossier.",
        "req status (human and --json) splits the verified bucket into genuine vs exempt so the headline number is not misleading by default.",
        "Safety requirements whose Verified status rests on an exemption are flagged distinctly, noting inherited SIL."
