      "id": "REQ-0142",
      "kind": "Functional",
      "links": [],
      "priority": "Must",
      "rationale": "An exempt or backfilled dossier makes Validation::passed() return true, so the 'Verified' status conflates grandfathered items with genuinely validated ones. Today 135 of 136 verified items rest only on a backfilled exemption yet are indistinguishable from real validation in req status, req sreq list, and req trace. Without a first-class provenance signal an agent or auditor is misled into trusting verification that has no analysis/test/statement behind it.",
      "statement": "req shall report the verification provenance of every requirement and safety requirement, distinguishing a genuine dossier from an audited exemption, a stale dossier, or an absent one.",
      "status": "Verified",
      "tags": [],
      "tests": [
