      "id": "REQ-0143",
      "kind": "Functional",
      "links": [],
      "priority": "Must",
      "rationale": "Safety requirements carry SIL obligations, so the audited backfill/no-dossier escape hatch that is acceptable for ordinary requirements is not acceptable for them. An exemption lets a high-integrity obligation reach Verified with no analysis, test, or statement behind it, which is exactly the false assurance the dossier exists to prevent.",
      "statement": "req shall require a genuine concluded validation dossier for any safety requirement that is Verified, rejecting an exempted or absent dossier as a substitute.",
      "status": "Verified",
      "tags": [],
